name: lolsplashart, League of Legends Splash Art Base
description:
High quality model trained for 400 hours on a 4090 on all League Splash Arts up till Snow Moon Skin Line.

huggingface: https://huggingface.co/Totsukawaii/LeagueBase/tree/main

PROS:

Diverse outputs/ Not overfitted ✔️

NAI base ✔️

Low Learning rate 3e-7 ✔️

High training resolution 2048x1152 ✔️

Better than all the overfitted models on civitai ✔️

CONS:

Slightly underfitted

Bad anatomy

Some outputs appear sunburned

Trained with inaccurate tagging - automatic tagging with wd14 tagger, blip

Cannot recreate original training images

*If using this model in your merge please include the recipe in your release.

Join my discord server - https://discord.gg/2RBWXFuVV6


Credits:

NAI - base model
Riot Games - artwork

Kohya ss sd scripts - trainer
